in
the
chamber
and
support
the
head
so
that
its
gasket
surface
is
level
.

Most
beakers
are
graduated
in
cubic
centimeters
(
cc.
)
,
making
it
necessary
to
convert
the
result
to
cubic
inches
.

Sometimes
