History
and
operation
of
the
motor
pool
.

Prior
to
1942
,
automobiles
were
the
individual
responsibility
of
the
agency
to
which
assigned
.

It
embraced
determining
when
to
purchase
and
when
to
trade
vehicles
,
who
was
to
drive
,
when
and
where
repairs
were
to
