was
transferred
,
by
Executive
Order
,
to
the
Division
of
Methods
,
Research
and
Office
Services
.

This
tied
in
closely
with
the
current
attempt
to
upgrade
state-owned
cars
to
the
extent
that
vehicles
are
not
retained
beyond
the
point
where
maintenance
