the
war
conferences
''
.

However
,
the
regionally
differentiated
results
,
which
appear
below
in
tables
,
are
interesting
evidence
of
the
problems
of
developing
self-government
under
even
the
most
favorable
circumstances
.

They
were
stressed
in
the
speeches
of
Si
Mubarak
Bekkai
when
the
first
Council
of
Ministers
was
formed
and
again
when
the
Istiqlal
took
a
